            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-rose-600 font-black text-2xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-base">Featured weddings blog = 3x more inbound referrals</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">Added "Real Weddings" blog with couple stories, venue details, planning tips, photo highlights. Month 1: 3.1x more organic traffic, 2x more referrals from vendors. Visible activity = in demand = top of mind = referrals = bookings.</p>
